ol.li: Detect overflow: New cell (55) doesn't fit in page 42

Redistribute cells:
Lower half stays in page 42 (10, 20, 30, 40, 50)
Upper half moves to page 99 (55, 60, 70, 80)
Promote separator: First key of right page (55) goes to parent
Update parent: Insert (55, ptr99) after existing (50, ptr42)
Link siblings: page 42 page 99 via right_sibling pointer
